source.name: Old Age, Survivors, and Disability Insurance (OASDI) Public-Use Microdata File, 2001 Data
source.description: The OASDI Public-Use Microdata File contains an extract of data fields from SSA's Master Beneficiary Record file and consists of a 1 percent random, representative sample of persons entitled to receive an OASDI benefit payment for December 2001. This file contains approximately 460,000 records, with 16 data fields on each record. Updated beneficiary information is also included in a sub-file of, Benefits Data for the Benefit and Earnings Public Use File, 2004 (Dataset Unique ID 56).
